</div>]]></content:encoded></item><item><title>KFC 超高解像炸雞相開放版權任下載     「盜圖者盜不走我們的味道」</title><link>https://unwire.hk/2022/03/31/kfc-2/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&amp;utm_medium=rss&amp;utm_campaign=kfc-2</link><dc:creator><![CDATA[Christy]]></dc:creator><pubDate>Thu, 31 Mar 2022 10:19:28 +0000</pubDate><category><![CDATA[科技趣聞]]></category><category><![CDATA[chickenstock]]></category><category><![CDATA[KFC]]></category><guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1093641</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>面對坊間的盜圖風氣， KFC 決定公開官方高清圖庫，把所有高清食物圖片開放版權，供大眾免費下載使用。更揶揄盜圖 [&#8230;]</p></p>]]></description><content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>面對坊間的盜圖風氣， KFC 決定公開官方高清圖庫，把所有高清食物圖片開放版權，供大眾免費下載使用。更揶揄盜圖者盜圖也盜不走 KFC 的味道，建議他們好好做，不要以低質盜圖損害 KFC 形象。</p><p>坊間有許多餐廳在未經許可的情況下，盜用 KFC 的炸雞照片作餐牌、宣傳等商業用途，希望利用「酥脆、多汁、有吸引力」的炸雞招徠。KFC 稱無法忍受解像度過低的盜圖，指盜圖的品質影響大眾對食物的觀感，即使看似美味，卻因解像度過低而大大減少吸引力。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093654" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38-1280x615.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38-768x369.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38-1536x738.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38-2048x984.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.38.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093653" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27-1280x615.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27-768x369.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27-1536x738.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27-2048x984.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.27.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093652" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57-1280x615.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57-768x369.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57-1536x738.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57-2048x984.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.07.57.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093655" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49-1280x615.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49-768x369.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49-1536x738.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49-2048x984.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.49.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p>除此之外，KFC 認為低質的盜圖亦會有損公司形象，因此索性於網站 chickenstock 公開官方高清圖庫，內含 KFC 旗下各式各樣的食物高清圖，解像度達 26861 x 18898，部份圖片檔案更高於 30MB，圖庫內的所有圖片已開放版權，供大眾免費下載使用。影片公開後 chickenstock 的網站隨即因流量過大而暫停運作，KFC 稱盜圖者較想像中多，會盡快做好準備，重新開放網站供盜圖者盜圖。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093658" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33-694x375.png" alt="" width="694" height="375" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33-694x375.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33-1280x692.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33-768x415.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33-1536x830.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33-2048x1106.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.10.33.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093657" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32-694x386.png" alt="" width="694" height="386" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32-694x386.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32-1280x711.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32-768x427.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32-1536x853.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32-2048x1138.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.09.32.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a> <a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093656" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59-694x333.png" alt="" width="694" height="333" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59-694x333.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59-1280x615.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59-768x369.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59-1536x738.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59-2048x984.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.08.59.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：影片截圖</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50.png"><img loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1093667" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50-694x341.png" alt="" width="694" height="341" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50-694x341.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50-1280x629.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50-768x378.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50-1536x755.png 1536w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50-2048x1007.png 2048w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/截圖-2022-03-31-10.22.50.png 1600w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p style="text-align: center;">圖片來源：chickenstock 截圖</p><p>KFC 於官方影片中表示，即使盜圖者盜取其食物圖片，但也偷不走 KFC 的口味，更把盜圖與原始圖片作比較，指這不是對待雞的方式，最後更警告盜圖者「想盜取我們的圖？可以，但請你好好做。」雖然影片看似為 chickenstock 圖庫作宣傳，卻更像在揶揄一眾盜圖者。</p><p><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_23762"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/yys_sVDSi6I?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://worldofbuzz.com/kfc-launches-free-image-bank-full-of-high-resolution-pictures-for-businesses-to-use/">WORLD OF BUZZ</a></p><p>—</p><p><u>unwire.hk </u>Mewe 專頁 : <a href="https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk"><u>https://mewe.com/p/unwirehk</u></a></p></p><div class="feedflare">
